-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to install the templates into FlashDevelop:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.) Start FlashDevelop
2.) When started click "Tools" -> "Application Files"
3.) In the explorer window that will open navigate into:
	-> Templates
		-> ProjectFiles
			-> AS3Project
	In this folder create a new folder named "AS3 Robotlegs Project"
4.) Copy the template files (*.fdt) into the currently created folder.


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to create a class file with the templates:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.) Open the "Project" view if not currently open
2.) Rightclick on the package where you want the new class to be created
	-> select "Add"
		-> "AS3 Robotlegs Project"
			-> the template you want to use